+- [Vector Store Pinecone](../../vector_store/VectorStorePinecone/VectorStorePinecone.node.md)
+- [Reranker Cohere](../RerankerCohere/RerankerCohere.node.md)
+- [AI Agent](../../agent/Agent.node.md)
